Variability (female) . Body black. Most specimens with yellowish streak along inner orbit only. Sometimes T2 and T3 or one of them basally with distinct or not obvious yellow spots. Specimens from Taiwan (
Ishikawa 1965a
) have yellow spots on the above mentioned structures, as well as on basal half of mandible, antero-laterally and dorso-posteriorly on pronotum, postero-laterally on lower metapleuron, upper part of metacoxa. Coloration of setae on T6 and S6 from brown to pale brown and sometimes almost whitish.
